.Dd October 15, 2007
.Dt CPC 4 evbppc
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm cpc
.Nd IBM CPC700 bridge support
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "cpc0 at mainbus0"
.Cd "com0 at cpc0 addr 0xff600300"
.Cd "com1 at cpc0 addr 0xff600400"
.Cd "pci0 at cpc0"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
provides support for the IBM CPC700 host bridge aimed at Power PC.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr com 4 ,
.Xr mainbus 4 ,
.Xr pci 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver
appeared in
.Nx 2.0 .
